SetInCountry: Indonesia
Category: A leap into the unknown
AuthorName: Sisca  Essa Riwana
AuthorCountry: Indonesia
Text: "in my old days I have a bad life style. I eat junk food, I smoke badly, I had\
  \ sex badly. \n\nI wanted to change my life style. \n\nSo I wanted to see the world\
  \ where there are no bad life style.\n\nI try to clean my environment but there\
  \ are no result, I tried to change the organization behavior but still there no\
  \ significant change\n\nHow can I change the environment where I live so I will\
  \ not infected by bad people\n\nI was hoping the land of the new world can make\
  \ my career better and better.\n\nI was hoping I can make my family happy and prosperous"
